To install Terraform, follow these steps:


SSH into your cloud server
sudo yum install -y zip unzip (if these are not installed)
wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.12.4/terraform_0.12.4_linux_amd64.zip
unzip terraform_0.12.4_linux_amd64.zip
sudo mv terraform /usr/local/bin/
Confirm terraform binary is accessible: terraform --version


Now add the following line to add terraform in PATH location.
export PATH="$PATH:/usr/local/bin/"

cd /etc
vi profile
source profile

 link for reference : https://github.com/Cloud-Yeti/aws-labs/tree/master/terraform-aws
